bill.summary: 5/19/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1994, the existing suspension of duty on butyl 2-(4-(5-trifluoromethyl-2-pyridinyloxy)phenoxy)propanoate) (also known as fluazifop-p-butyl).
